data.description: This newer built, beautiful cream brick home is located convenient to shopping, dining and recreation.  It has a brand new privacy fence on .47 acre lot.  The home is an open floor plan with fireplace and fantastic island in kitchen.  Beautiful lighting and a split floor plan.  Primary bedroom has bathroom with double vanity and walk in closet.  The flooring throughout the home is vinyl planking.  The front porch is very inviting and plenty of privacy in the backyard for entertaining.  All this on one level with small step up from garage to have your shopping straight into kitchen area.  Do not miss out on this fabulous deal.  Contact listing agent or your own realtor to set up showing.
